  <h2>Community</h2>

  <div class="content">
    <p>
	<span style="line-height: 20px; ">Please consider joining our&nbsp;</span><a href="http://www.facebook.com/pages/Brain-Preservation-Foundation/142229665787206">Facebook page</a>&nbsp;<span style="line-height: 20px; ">(social networking), our&nbsp;</span><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/groups/Brain-Preservation-Foundation-4489503">LinkedIn group</a> (professional networking),<span style="line-height: 20px; ">&nbsp;and/or our&nbsp;</span><a href="http://twitter.com/lets_upgrade">Twitter feed</a>&nbsp;(brief news updates).<span style="line-height: 20px; ">&nbsp;T</span>he more practical, open-minded, future oriented, and rational folks who join the BPF community, the faster we can achieve our ambitious goals. Thanks for connecting!</p>
